cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the security of autonomous vehicles and proposes an intrusion detection system to identify cyber-attacks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the proposed system is based on machine learning models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses ensemble learning and feature selection approaches to improve the performance of the intrusion detection system. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of Vehicle-to-everything (V2X) technology for communication among vehicles and other infrastructures. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper proposes a software-based solution for intrusion detection in AV networks.
